Package com.IAppDevelopment.virtual_marathon.Race

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Home
    This class is designed to process the time data downloaded from the server, And move them to the display, In addition, we will get from the user the desired distance for the target end he has chosen, And we will pass this figure by saving it locally.
    Race
    This class is the class from which the race begins, the class processes data of time, distance, in addition to data that is updated on the map
